                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>New York</placeName>\n                <date>Sept 16<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> 1862</date>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>31 Nassau St.</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p><addressee>I. Leeser Esq.</addressee>\n                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Dear Sir,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Your letter of yesterday<lb/> is at hand. Enclosed find $2.62, <hi\n                    rend=\"underline\">large</hi><lb/> amount of <persName>Mr Loewe's</persName>\n                indebtedness.</p>\n            <p>When I first wrote you I was under the<lb/> impression that <persName>Mr\n                    Loewe</persName> owed you<lb/> a balance, independent of the advertisement<lb/>\n                last inserted. Your receipted bill being<lb/> only for the latter, of course\n                satisfies me to<lb/> the contrary. Your commission to <persName>Mr<lb/>\n                    Isaacs</persName> with your regards to <persName>Mr Loewe</persName> will<lb/>\n                both be attended to.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">Yours Respectfully</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\"><persName role=\"author\">Joseph H. Levy</persName>.</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p39p2ws3z/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
